rComments: A nice guy who cared about the students, but he takes WAY too long to cover a concept. The lecture was 2 hours long and could have been covered in an hour. In addition, handwriting was sometimes indecipherable. Class was a snooze fest.
Great professor, he really cares about his students.  He goes out of his way to explain the material as clearly as he can and is always eager to make sure his students understand.
Very passionate teacher. I only wish his powerpoints were of any use.
